{"tid":899410,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓市新低】屯門麗寶大廈劈價21%易手","createTime":"2018-11-12T11:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T13:57:05.000Z","uid":174649,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"58d428e139b29c12d81a2901e705dff14bf56f45","tid":899410,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181112/large/1542022290_1018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181112%2Flarge%2F1542022290_1018.jpg&h=bf39b8d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門私樓「單幢三寶」再錄劈價。<br />\n<br />\n消息指麗寶大廈高層G室，實用面積248方呎，今年9月樓市最高位放盤，叫價398萬元，兩日前減至350萬元仍無人問津，直至近日由高位計累減21%至315萬元終沽出，呎價12,702元，成交價創屋苑今年新低。賣方2015年8月以280萬元買入單位，持貨3年升值僅13%。<br />\n<br />\n中原成交紀錄顯示，麗寶大廈高層H室，實用面積239方呎，今年6月癲賣403萬元，呎價16,862元，屬該廈首宗及唯一升破400萬元成交。"},{"pid":"bc42b076b5445394322e541d72b4290e1f4049c5","tid":899410,"uid":122377,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"廢閪三寶 唔計"},{"pid":"5dd80815b36ce027f998c43bf92f158f4dfe49bb","tid":899410,"uid":41196,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:57:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾三寶都12000蚊呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902074183d6e436a065826168bba11a41165bfb1","tid":899410,"uid":57005,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:58:12.000Z","msg":"屯門三寶都仲要尺價過萬，嘉湖會唔會好D？"},{"pid":"d3a713fd66136981939fac3008559974af562e29","tid":899410,"uid":35656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T12:07:24.000Z","msg":"廢閪三寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641aa1dd2255c91429bcb13b0161a09aa522ac88","tid":899410,"uid":159313,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"今年6月癲賣403萬元，呎價16,862元，屬該廈首宗及唯一升破400萬元成交。<br />\n<br />\n希望唔係連登低智仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gi